TextBody:
Hello Naveen,

Thank you for your patience regarding this case.

We have received an update from our Engineering team and they recommend us to schedule a remote session to check if the situation persist after we remove the URL categories. 

Also, if it is necessary to use the URL categories, then we need to use virustotal.com as entry. 

Please let us know your availability for the next week, so we can schedule a new session.

Looking forward for your response.

Best regards,
__________________
Daniel Anton | Technical Support Engineer

DLP | MDM | Device Control | Content Aware Protection
